law.history: Repealed 1978 Ky. Acts ch. 45, sec. 2, effective January 1, 1978. -- Amended 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 177, sec. 2. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 367.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Fees allowed Commonwealth's witnesses in felony cases.
